ith all the new variants available, the Matryoshka dolls are ultimately rooted in tradition, and are generally still gifted as such. These gorgeous handmade dolls have become the stuff of legends among people who value their meaning behind motherhood, family, moral values, fertility and abundance. Gifting one of these beautiful doll sets is not just a gift to simply add to your room decor, it's a gift of love, care and of the heart for your warm hearth."]
